<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wulan Novia Boba Milk Tea | Segar & Lezat</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&family=Pacifico&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary-teal: #4CB5B5;
            --secondary-cream: #FDF8F1;
            --dark-chocolate: #4D3327;
            --accent-brown: #8D6E63;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--secondary-cream);
            color: var(--dark-chocolate);
        }

        .brand-font {
            font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
        }

        .bg-teal-custom { background-color: var(--primary-teal); }
        .text-teal-custom { color: var(--primary-teal); }
        .border-teal-custom { border-color: var(--primary-teal); }

        .banner-clip {
            border-radius: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }

        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .whatsapp-float {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 100;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-teal-custom/20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-teal-custom flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl">
                    <i class="fas fa-bubble-tea"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-teal-custom brand-font">Wulan Novia</span>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-6 font-semibold">
                <a href="#home" class="hover:text-teal-custom">Home</a>
                <a href="#menu" class="hover:text-teal-custom">Menu</a>
                <a href="#topping" class="hover:text-teal-custom">Topping</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-teal-custom">Kontak</a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wa.me/628893620711" target="_blank" class="bg-teal-custom text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:opacity-90 transition">
                Pesan Sekarang
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="home" class="py-10 md:py-20 container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
                <span class="inline-block bg-teal-custom/10 text-teal-custom px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Fresh & Delicious
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
                    Nikmati Kesegaran <br>
                    <span class="text-teal-custom brand-font">Boba Wulan Novia!</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-lg">
                    Manisnya pas, bobanya kenyal, dan harganya ramah di kantong. Pilihan terbaik untuk menemani harimu yang seru!
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/628893620711" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-teal-custom text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/30 hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-2xl"></i>
                        Pesan via WhatsApp
                    </a>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 border-2 border-dashed border-accent-brown/30 rounded-2xl">
                        <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-brown italic">Mulai Rp 5.000</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 pt-4">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-custom"></i> 100% Gula Asli</span>
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-custom"></i> Boba Kenyal</span>
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-custom"></i> Bahan Premium</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative max-w-[320px]">
